summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Path of Exile 2 Passive Skill Tree planner. All major functionality working correctly including canvas rendering, UI controls, and navigation.

ui_bugs.issue: Duplicate data-testid 'export-build-btn' found on two different buttons
ui_bugs.details: One button in canvas controls toolbar and another in sidebar actions section both use same test ID

passed_tests: Homepage loads correctly at /en without errors
Game selection (PoE 2 vs Diablo IV) works properly
Canvas skill tree renders with 2546+ nodes visible
Build name input field accepts and displays text
Zoom controls (zoom in, zoom out, reset) function properly
Search toggle button shows/hides search input
Search input accepts text and filters nodes
Character Stats sidebar displays all categories (Defensive, Attributes, Offensive, Damage)
Navigation between homepage and build planner works
Responsive design and visual styling is excellent
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix duplicate data-testid issue: The export-build-btn test ID is used on two different buttons. Consider renaming one to 'export-build-canvas-btn' and the other to 'export-build-sidebar-btn' for better test specificity.
